The wordpress of php frameworks

Features
- one definition file
- html templates
- MvC
- very small footprint
- simple
- neat

How it works

Design your app
Create a complete html mockup


Templating the app
Spaghetti assumes you have taken the time to create a complete html mockup of your website

Design->Mockup->Integrate->Code

